body:
I've been having a problem with my account for a while now, for some reason whenever i try to log into the riot game support website it redirects me to a page that says that i've been signed out. It's problematic since i sort of wanted to get one of the offers from my shop. This has been a problem for about a year now, but i've ignored it since it's not that big a deal and i haven't really needed to contact support for anything.

I suspect it may be because of my compromised email, the email that i made my account with got malaware'd or hacked by a bot, and started sending spam emails to everyone i've ever emailed, including riot support. Since then i've made a new email and linked it to my league of legends account, but this is the only thing i can think of that could be the reason.

Would someone be able to look into why i can't log into support? i would send a support ticket, but you kinda need to log in to do that {{sticker:zombie-nunu-bummed}}
